Detailed Description

template<class KEY, class ITEM, class COLLECTION, class ITERATOR>
class ACE_RMCast_Copy_On_Write< KEY, ITEM, COLLECTION, ITERATOR >

Implement a copy on write wrapper for a map-like collection.
